<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-a-word">in a word</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>总之；简言之；一句话：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In a word, good listening can really enable us to get closer to each other.
总之，认真倾听确实能使我们拉近彼此的距离。</p><footer>2008 江苏书面表达</footer></div></div>